</p>
<p class="content-text">
    The system returns a table of all registered deeds matching your criteria. Each row shows the Document Number, Date of Registration, Nature of Deed (sale, mortgage, release, partition, gift, power of attorney), the executing and claiming parties, and the consideration value. If no results are returned, the system shows a Nil Encumbrance response. For a certified copy, click Apply Online, log into your registered account, confirm the search parameters, and proceed to the fee payment page. After payment confirmation, the SRO processes the request and the signed PDF is available in your account within 3 to 7 working days. Use the <strong><a href="https://econline.in/">ec online</a></strong> TN section for the latest portal updates.
</p>

