<h2>Verifying property title with Patta, Chitta, and Villangam EC</h2>
<p class="content-text">
    A complete title search in Tamil Nadu requires cross-verifying multiple documents. The three pillars of land verification are Patta (ownership record), Chitta (village register showing extents), and the Villangam EC (transaction record). When you perform a search, you get the list of all registered transactions. However, you must match this list against the revenue records. Please prepare all details to ensure a successful search on the <strong><a href="https://econline.in/">ec online</a></strong> system.
</p>
