</p>
<p class="content-text">
    Through the Registration Department system, performing a <strong><a href="https://econline.in/">ec online</a></strong> search is standard to verify property titles. If transactions occurred within the query period, the Sub-Registrar Office issues a Form 15. If no records exist, they issue Form 16, representing a Nil Encumbrance Certificate.
