<h2>Cross-verifying Bhoomi RTC / Khata mutation with your EC</h2>
<p class="content-text">
    A comprehensive property title check involves cross-verifying the EC with mutation records. The EC shows transaction history, but the mutation register shows owner details recognized by revenue authorities (e.g. Bhoomi RTC/Khata).
</p>
<p class="content-text">
    Ensure that the seller name in the registered sale deed matches the latest entry in the Khata database. If there is a mismatch, the mutation has not been completed. This mismatch can block future transactions or bank loan approvals. Once transaction details match, select the <strong><a href="https://econline.in/">ec online</a></strong> certified copy option to download the legally certified PDF copy.
</p>

