<h2>Common reasons why EC applications get rejected</h2>
<p class="content-text">
    Understanding common rejection reasons helps you submit a clean application on the first attempt. The most frequent reasons include:
</p>
<ul class="guide-list" style="margin-left: 2rem; color: #475569; line-height: 1.8;">
    <li><strong>Wrong SRO selected:</strong> The SRO must match the district and locality where the property is registered. Check the parent sale deed to confirm the SRO name.</li>
    <li><strong>Incorrect survey number:</strong> Survey numbers must match the revenue map exactly. Even a digit difference causes rejection.</li>
