<h2>Overview of Telangana land records search portals</h2>
<p class="content-text">
    The state of Telangana administers land records through two main online platforms. The Registration and Stamps Department portal manages the registration of deeds, mortgages, and encumbrance logs for both agricultural and non-agricultural properties. Additionally, the Dharani portal serves as the integrated land records management system, focusing primarily on agricultural holdings.
</p>
<p class="content-text">
