<h2>Verifying Revenue Records with Patta Chitta</h2>
<p class="content-text">
    Besides the encumbrance registry, you must check ownership entries in the revenue databases. In Tamil Nadu, the revenue records are known as Patta (land ownership record) and Chitta (land dimensions and type details).
</p>
<p class="content-text">
    The name on the latest registered sale deed must match the owner name on the Patta document. If they do not match, you must apply for a Patta transfer. Buying land without a clear Patta in the seller name makes future property transactions difficult.
</p>
<p class="content-text">
